---
// Footer.astro - Footer Premium
---

<footer class="w-full border-t border-white/5 bg-[#0D0D11]/90 py-12 relative z-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
    
    <!-- Left: Credits -->
    <div class="text-center md:text-left">
      <span class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-white font-heading block mb-1">
        Brayant<span class="text-blue-300 font-extrabold">.F</span>
      </span>
      <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 font-light font-heading">
        Diseñado & Desarrollado por Brayant Flores © 2026. Todos los derechos reservados.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Center: Availability Status (Premium ping animation) -->
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/10 px-4 py-1.5 shadow-lg">
      <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
        <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-emerald-400 opacity-75"></span>
        <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-emerald-500"></span>
      </span>
      <span class="text-[10px] font-mono font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-400">
        Disponible para proyectos
      </span>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: Social Links -->
    <div class="flex gap-6 items-center">
      <a
        href="https://www.instagram.com/brayan_tsj/"
        target="_blank"
        class="text-xs font-heading font-semibold text-zinc-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 relative py-1 group"
      >
        Instagram
        <span class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-0 h-[1px] bg-white group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-300"></span>
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/brayant-flores/"
        target="_blank"
        class="text-xs font-heading font-semibold text-zinc-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 relative py-1 group"
      >
        LinkedIn
        <span class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-0 h-[1px] bg-white group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-300"></span>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</footer>